1
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,200
(A new excitement...)

2
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:35,600
(and a long-awaited date)

3
00:00:35,900 --> 00:00:38,410
(How pretty.)

4
00:00:38,610 --> 00:00:41,810
(The trusted future son-in-law has a change of heart?)

5
00:00:42,010 --> 00:00:44,850
(I can't remember a thing before the person I like.)

6
00:00:46,510 --> 00:00:48,920
(Yu Bin and Hee Dong are growing closer.)

7
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:51,190
(Yu Bin and Yoon Hoo begin to drift apart.)

8
00:00:51,290 --> 00:00:53,190
- Can I take a look at it?
- Si Woo.

9
00:00:54,290 --> 00:00:56,730
(Si Woo sees the couple photo of Hee Dong and Yu Bin.)

10
00:00:57,590 --> 00:00:58,690
I'll be right back.

11
00:00:59,130 --> 00:01:01,630
(Yu Bin.)

12
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:05,169
(Si Woo asks to talk to Yu Bin.)

13
00:01:05,170 --> 00:01:06,500
She asked to talk.

14
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:08,800
(I bet the two will get into a fight.)

15
00:01:09,100 --> 00:01:11,940
(Girls' talk, including Seo Yoon)

16
00:01:11,970 --> 00:01:15,980
When I said, "You don't remember what you said yesterday."

17
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:22,420
(Hee Dong said, "I can't remember a thing before the person I like.")

18
00:01:24,090 --> 00:01:25,720
(I don't know how he's feeling.)

19
00:01:26,190 --> 00:01:30,130
(Yu Bin is confused about Hee Dong's feelings.)

20
00:01:30,230 --> 00:01:31,929
(Yu Bin and Seo Yoon)

21
00:01:31,930 --> 00:01:33,260
It's Eun Byul.

22
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,170
Say, for example,

23
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:42,639
if Seo Yoon and Si Woo were in my situation,

24
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,440
who would you choose?

25
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,680
(Thinking)

26
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,310
Is it something like this?

27
00:01:51,450 --> 00:01:56,549
The kind of person you usually prefer?

28
00:01:56,550 --> 00:01:58,819
And the kind of person who likes me more?

29
00:01:58,820 --> 00:02:00,120
Is it or not?

30
00:02:00,660 --> 00:02:02,459
It's not like...

31
00:02:02,460 --> 00:02:04,259
I don't have feelings for Hoo.

32
00:02:04,260 --> 00:02:06,460
- True.
- Here's why.

33
00:02:06,490 --> 00:02:10,029
Hee Dong flirts in a teasing way,

34
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,399
while Hoo is...

35
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,600
straightforward and honest.

36
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:16,539
But the thing is,

37
00:02:16,540 --> 00:02:20,080
Hee Dong is my ideal type, appearance-wise.

38
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:22,680
So...

39
00:02:23,810 --> 00:02:26,409
- It's tough.
- For real.

40
00:02:26,410 --> 00:02:29,079
Getting along really well like friends versus heart-fluttering.

41
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,650
It doesn't boil down to that.

42
00:02:33,490 --> 00:02:36,389
Both dates were great.

43
00:02:36,390 --> 00:02:39,059
- It'd be weird if she didn't waver.
- Exactly.

44
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:41,499
As Yu Bin gets to know others,

45
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:42,599
she'll realize...

46
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:44,499
- how dear Yoon Hoo is.
- Of course.

47
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:46,370
- Looks don't last long.
- I see.

48
00:02:47,940 --> 00:02:50,539
Si Woo is a part of...

49
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:52,909
Yu Bin's relationship advice session.

50
00:02:52,910 --> 00:02:54,579
- I know, right?
- Yu Bin might feel...

51
00:02:54,580 --> 00:02:56,079
- She must feel uneasy.
- conflicted.

52
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:58,649
It's uncomfortable for both of them. Don't you agree?

53
00:02:58,650 --> 00:02:59,680
Yes.

54
00:03:00,350 --> 00:03:04,290
(Episode 6: Timing)

55
00:03:06,250 --> 00:03:12,230
(Yet again, they receive a text message.)

56
00:03:13,500 --> 00:03:15,829
"Send the name of the resident who made..."

57
00:03:15,830 --> 00:03:17,769
"your heart flutter today."

58
00:03:17,770 --> 00:03:20,870
"The text will not be delivered today."

59
00:03:22,770 --> 00:03:24,170
What a twist.

60
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:26,370
I'm sure they'd want to know the results.

61
00:03:27,510 --> 00:03:30,850
(It could be the time to be more honest.)

62
00:03:31,380 --> 00:03:34,980
(To whom are their feelings headed?)

63
00:03:36,890 --> 00:03:38,220
I think...

64
00:03:38,650 --> 00:03:40,760
I sent it within seconds.

65
00:03:42,220 --> 00:03:43,729
- Who did Eun Byul choose?
- Who?

66
00:03:43,730 --> 00:03:45,689
- Who do you think she chose?
- Jae Hyuk.

67
00:03:45,690 --> 00:03:46,759
- Jae Hyuk?
- Yes.

68
00:03:46,760 --> 00:03:48,729
Are you sure it's not who you want?

69
00:03:48,730 --> 00:03:50,530
I prefer Jae Seung.

70
00:03:50,570 --> 00:03:52,329
- Bravo.
- I see.

71
00:03:52,330 --> 00:03:53,639
(Glancing)

72
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:54,770
For real?

73
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:57,509
- All of a sudden...
- If you react...

74
00:03:57,510 --> 00:03:59,140
to every single comment...

75
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,509
Don't bully me.

76
00:04:00,510 --> 00:04:02,940
Exactly. At this rate, we can't ask questions.

77
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:07,520
(Who did Eun Byul choose?)

78
00:04:07,550 --> 00:04:09,580
(Shin Jae Hyuk)

79
00:04:09,780 --> 00:04:12,589
(Cho Eun Byul chose Shin Jae Hyuk for the Attraction Selection.)

80
00:04:12,590 --> 00:04:16,159
So far, I get along...

81
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:18,890
with Jae Hyuk more.

82
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:22,100
- It's Shin Jae Hyuk.
- You're right.

83
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,470
- It's Jae Hyuk.
- Jae Hyuk.

84
00:04:24,230 --> 00:04:26,100
Eun Byul's mom's hunch was right.

85
00:04:26,730 --> 00:04:29,000
(Who will Seo Yoon choose?)

86
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:33,479
I didn't contemplate for a long time.

87
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:37,450
The name I should send popped up in my head right away.

88
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,019
(Shin Jae Hyuk)

89
00:04:42,020 --> 00:04:44,890
(Woo Seo Yoon chose Shin Jae Hyuk for the Attraction Selection.)

90
00:04:45,350 --> 00:04:47,860
First off, it was a lot more fun.

91
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:49,990
We got along really well.

92
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:53,260
I felt comfortable around him from the beginning.

93
00:04:55,230 --> 00:04:59,070
(Eun Byul and Seo Yoon both chose Jae Hyuk.)

94
00:04:59,330 --> 00:05:01,039
(Congratulations, Jae Hyuk got 2 votes!)

95
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,970
- Suddenly...
- What a surprise.

96
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:05,260
His strategy is finally working from zero votes.

97
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:07,810
- He's gotten the hang of it.
- I see.

98
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:10,450
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

99
00:05:11,410 --> 00:05:12,549
Everyone...

100
00:05:12,550 --> 00:05:14,179
ends up voting for Jae Hyuk...

101
00:05:14,180 --> 00:05:15,619
after a date with him.

102
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:16,819
- You're right.
- Exactly.

103
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:18,389
Jae Hyuk is quite charming.

104
00:05:18,390 --> 00:05:20,889
- He's charming.
- Yes, he's full of charms.

105
00:05:20,890 --> 00:05:21,989
Jae Hyuk is charming.

106
00:05:21,990 --> 00:05:24,429
Jae Seung has gotten no votes...

107
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:25,950
despite going on dates with the girls.

108
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,759
(Disappointed)

109
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:30,170
Get some fresh air if you feel uneasy.

110
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:33,099
The results don't seem promising.

111
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:34,340
Should we change dads?

112
00:05:35,770 --> 00:05:40,880
(Who will Jae Hyuk, who got two votes, choose?)

113
00:05:42,040 --> 00:05:43,680
I couldn't decide.

114
00:05:43,750 --> 00:05:45,250
I had a lot on my mind.

115
00:05:45,780 --> 00:05:49,180
Yesterday's date with Eun Byul was great.

116
00:05:50,350 --> 00:05:52,889
But after the date with Seo Yoon today,

117
00:05:52,890 --> 00:05:54,660
that was nice too.

118
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:59,630
What should I...

119
00:06:00,700 --> 00:06:03,199
I have no idea what to do.

120
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:06,029
The two have opposite charms.

121
00:06:06,030 --> 00:06:07,340
(Eun Byul and Seo Yoon)

122
00:06:09,540 --> 00:06:12,070
Having to choose only one person...

123
00:06:12,170 --> 00:06:13,270
was tough.

124
00:06:15,610 --> 00:06:19,910
(Unable to choose without hesitation)

125
00:06:20,850 --> 00:06:23,480
(Meanwhile, there's another who can't decide.)

126
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:26,850
I'm kind of lost.

127
00:06:27,290 --> 00:06:30,659
My date with Hee Dong...

128
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:33,160
made me feel new emotions.

129
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:37,329
Meanwhile, I thought...

130
00:06:37,330 --> 00:06:39,899
I was just comfortable and used to being with Hoo...

131
00:06:39,900 --> 00:06:42,340
up until yesterday.

132
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:45,509
But after my date with Hee Dong today...

133
00:06:45,510 --> 00:06:46,539
I'll protect you.

134
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:48,239
Hoo proactively expressed...

135
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,649
his feelings more than expected yesterday,

136
00:06:50,650 --> 00:06:54,580
which made my heart flutter more.

137
00:06:55,850 --> 00:06:56,919
And so,

138
00:06:56,920 --> 00:07:01,559
I couldn't decide who to choose for the Attraction Selection.

139
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,866
(Feeling conflicted after the dates)

140
00:07:02,890 --> 00:07:04,330
I even thought that...

141
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:08,800
choosing both was for the better.

142
00:07:09,900 --> 00:07:10,999
- Stop.
- No.

143
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,600
(Choose both?)

144
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:17,070
To think you and I are on the same page here. Gosh.

145
00:07:19,340 --> 00:07:22,679
(Meanwhile, Hee Dong, who went on a date with Yu Bin)

146
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:26,949
Yu Bin made today's date relaxed.

147
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:28,380
Pose like we're close friends.

148
00:07:31,450 --> 00:07:32,649
Okay, pass.

149
00:07:32,650 --> 00:07:36,020
I could tell she was trying to get along with me.

150
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:40,360
Yu Bin, with whom I had fun during the date,

151
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,030
was on my mind.

152
00:07:42,230 --> 00:07:45,330
- She was on his mind.
- On his mind.

153
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:48,840
(What about Yoon Hoo?)

154
00:07:50,370 --> 00:07:52,340
Today, I'm not sure.

155
00:07:52,810 --> 00:07:54,739
During the date,

156
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:57,649
I was more focused on Si Woo.

157
00:07:57,650 --> 00:08:00,919
But at the same time, I'm still interested in Yu Bin.

158
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:03,720
So I'm not entirely sure yet.

159
00:08:04,490 --> 00:08:06,719
- My gosh.
- I thought he wouldn't waver.

160
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:08,059
- I know, right?
- He's wavering.

161
00:08:08,060 --> 00:08:10,259
- He may have a change of heart.
- We even told them...

162
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,459
to fix the wedding date.

163
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:13,059
Yu Bin and Yoon Hoo are wavering.

164
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:14,930
(Yu Bin and Yoon Hoo waver.)

165
00:08:16,030 --> 00:08:21,440
(After emotions ran high, making a decision only got tougher.)

166
00:08:23,710 --> 00:08:26,039
- This is tiresome.
- Is it?

167
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:28,109
Si Woo also has a lot on her mind.

168
00:08:28,110 --> 00:08:30,040
I thought about it for a long time.

169
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:31,750
Why?

170
00:08:32,380 --> 00:08:34,119
Because he said...

171
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,780
he doesn't remember a thing before the person he likes.

172
00:08:37,850 --> 00:08:40,150
For Hee Dong to say such a thing with his personality.

173
00:08:41,490 --> 00:08:42,890
What is he thinking?

174
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:47,330
Did his feelings change?

175
00:08:48,830 --> 00:08:53,600
So I wasn't sure if Hee Dong was my top choice.

176
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:04,350
But to say Yoon Hoo was my top choice,

177
00:09:05,210 --> 00:09:07,220
I still had feelings for Hee Dong.

178
00:09:09,380 --> 00:09:12,750
I contemplated until the last minute, said "Whatever..."

179
00:09:13,450 --> 00:09:14,690
Whatever.

180
00:09:14,990 --> 00:09:16,220
And sent the text.

181
00:09:16,660 --> 00:09:18,530
Today's not the final day.

182
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:21,299
- You Hee Dong.
- Hee Dong. As expected.

183
00:09:21,300 --> 00:09:22,300
(Si Woo chose Hee Dong.)

184
00:09:22,301 --> 00:09:24,330
- Really.
- Si Woo is cool.

185
00:09:25,370 --> 00:09:27,439
Si Woo could've taken what he said to heart.

186
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,169
She could've lost her temper by saying...

187
00:09:29,170 --> 00:09:30,839
- "What? You don't remember?" - Even so.

188
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:33,670
But Si Woo stuck to her feelings until the end.

189
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:35,010
Exactly.

190
00:09:40,880 --> 00:09:43,320
(Hee Dong sent a name after much contemplation.)

191
00:09:44,090 --> 00:09:47,420
(Who did Hee Dong choose?)

192
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:54,260
(Tonight was particularly chaotic.)

193
00:09:57,600 --> 00:10:02,070
(After much thinking, everyone has chosen someone.)

194
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,170
Si Woo chose Hee Dong.

195
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:05,769
Eun Byul and Seo Yoon chose...

196
00:10:05,770 --> 00:10:07,439
- Jae Hyuk.
- Jae Hyuk.

197
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:10,449
(Attraction Selection)

198
00:10:10,450 --> 00:10:12,350
- What?
- What about the rest?

199
00:10:12,410 --> 00:10:14,349
Why won't you tell us?

200
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:16,149
- For real?
- What?

201
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:18,019
- Hold on.
- Why only show some...

202
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:19,889
and not the rest?

203
00:10:19,890 --> 00:10:21,660
- Show us everything.
- Exactly.

204
00:10:23,490 --> 00:10:25,159
- It looks delicious.
- Nice.

205
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:26,930
(After the tough selection time)

206
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:29,159
- Here it is.
- It smells amazing.

207
00:10:29,160 --> 00:10:31,630
(The kids have gathered for some late-night snacks.)

208
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:35,099
- It looks good.
- Does it not need to be reheated?

209
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:36,169
(Yu Bin's cream risotto...)

210
00:10:36,170 --> 00:10:37,786
(and Jae Hyuk's stir-fried assorted seafood)

211
00:10:37,810 --> 00:10:39,710
It's 10:17pm.

212
00:10:40,170 --> 00:10:42,410
- Dinner, right?
- It's a late-night snack.

213
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,580
Right.

214
00:10:45,410 --> 00:10:48,379
(Jae Hyuk sits in front of Seo Yoon.)

215
00:10:48,380 --> 00:10:50,179
To face Seo Yoon.

216
00:10:50,180 --> 00:10:51,720
- I know, right?
- Exactly.

217
00:10:52,190 --> 00:10:53,620
There were many empty seats.

218
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:56,820
- You feel the pressure, right?
- Yes.

219
00:10:58,030 --> 00:10:59,190
How much would you like?

220
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:01,800
(Glancing)

221
00:11:01,801 --> 00:11:02,900
- Me?
- Yes.

222
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:04,270
What is it?

223
00:11:05,630 --> 00:11:07,100
Scrape it off, please.

224
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:09,400
It won't be bad, right?

225
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:12,109
- The taste?
- Yes, the taste.

226
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:13,170
Shall I dig in?

227
00:11:13,710 --> 00:11:15,080
- Do you mind?
- No.

228
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:21,050
(Impressed)

229
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:23,280
It's actually good.

230
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:24,920
What is it?

231
00:11:25,290 --> 00:11:26,920
- I'm serious.
- Thank you.

232
00:11:26,990 --> 00:11:27,990
A lot?

233
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:31,490
(Trying another piece)

234
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:34,329
- It's really good.
- Thank you.

235
00:11:34,330 --> 00:11:37,800
I was surprised when you added starch.

236
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,399
But that's normal.

237
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:41,400
Don't you use starch when you're cooking full-on?

238
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:43,300
Don't you find it good too?

239
00:11:43,470 --> 00:11:45,109
No, it's too bland for me.

240
00:11:45,110 --> 00:11:46,170
Really?

241
00:11:47,740 --> 00:11:49,410
What did everyone do today?

242
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,520
We...

243
00:11:57,350 --> 00:12:02,120
went to the arcade, played some games,

244
00:12:02,590 --> 00:12:06,730
and had tteokbokki at a snack stand.

245
00:12:10,330 --> 00:12:13,629
We swam outdoors.

246
00:12:13,630 --> 00:12:14,669
Sorry?

247
00:12:14,670 --> 00:12:17,169
- It was freezing cold.
- Seriously?

248
00:12:17,170 --> 00:12:19,070
- He was topless.
- Really?

249
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:21,040
- You're lying.
- No, I'm not.

250
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:23,480
So I got changed.

251
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:24,910
No, for real?

252
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,020
Can I tell the others?

253
00:12:29,180 --> 00:12:31,620
- Isn't that too much?
- So no?

254
00:12:34,790 --> 00:12:35,960
It was...

255
00:12:36,290 --> 00:12:38,459
- Eun Byul.
- Oh, dear.

256
00:12:38,460 --> 00:12:40,330
- Eun Byul is bothered.
- Eun Byul.

257
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:42,059
Look at Eun Byul's eyes.

258
00:12:42,060 --> 00:12:44,099
- Look at them.
- How fierce.

259
00:12:44,100 --> 00:12:45,169
(Eun Byul's eyes look intense.)

260
00:12:45,170 --> 00:12:46,269
To think she could look like that.

261
00:12:46,270 --> 00:12:48,499
Just look at her eyes.

262
00:12:48,500 --> 00:12:52,339
My daughter fell on her buttocks in a roller rink...

263
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:55,439
while the other girl got to be all warm in the water.

264
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,809
