- A sleep mask.

327
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:19,610
Thank you.

328
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:22,109
Tell me if you need more after trying it.

329
00:17:22,110 --> 00:17:24,779
Can I have all of them?

330
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:26,480
Try it first tonight.

331
00:17:28,550 --> 00:17:30,279
What time will you sleep...

332
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:31,519
tonight?

333
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:32,850
I'm not sure.

334
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:39,490
How was it today?

335
00:17:40,090 --> 00:17:42,330
Earlier, I couldn't hear quite clearly.

336
00:17:43,060 --> 00:17:44,100
Is that so?

337
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:45,470
Where are you going?

338
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,800
- How about we chat more?
- Sure.

339
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:50,770
How about here?

340
00:17:52,210 --> 00:17:53,240
Here?

341
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:56,310
- Or upstairs?
- Let's go upstairs.

342
00:17:56,740 --> 00:17:57,780
Right.

343
00:17:58,350 --> 00:18:02,780
(Eun Byul asked to talk with Jae Hyuk.)

344
00:18:05,690 --> 00:18:08,459
What a surprise from Eun Byul.

345
00:18:08,460 --> 00:18:10,189
To think Eun Byul would go for it like that.

346
00:18:10,190 --> 00:18:12,429
