349
00:18:15,607 --> 00:18:16,737
How about here?

350
00:18:18,377 --> 00:18:19,407
Here?

351
00:18:19,907 --> 00:18:21,977
- Or upstairs?
- Let's go upstairs.

352
00:18:22,877 --> 00:18:23,947
Right.

353
00:18:24,517 --> 00:18:28,987
(Eun Byul asked to talk with Jae Hyuk.)

354
00:18:30,217 --> 00:18:31,886
(Shocked)

355
00:18:31,887 --> 00:18:34,586
What a surprise from Eun Byul.

356
00:18:34,587 --> 00:18:36,326
To think Eun Byul would go for it like that.

357
00:18:36,327 --> 00:18:38,556
While Seo Yoon has left the living room.

358
00:18:38,557 --> 00:18:40,096
- Right?
- Seizing an opening.

359
00:18:40,097 --> 00:18:41,126
She's pushing forward.

360
00:18:41,127 --> 00:18:42,996
By the way, Eun Dol's...

361
00:18:42,997 --> 00:18:44,066
- Eun Dol?
- My bad.

362
00:18:44,067 --> 00:18:46,096
- Who's Eun Dol?
- Hold on.

363
00:18:46,097 --> 00:18:48,036
I'm sorry.

364
00:18:48,037 --> 00:18:49,406
I meant Eun Byul.

365
00:18:49,407 --> 00:18:51,737
Byul and Dol are very different.

366
00:18:52,237 --> 00:18:53,276
(Apologizing)

367
00:18:53,277 --> 00:18:55,206
- I...
- They thought hard about that name.

368
00:18:55,207 --> 00:18:57,206
I would understand if you had said Eon Byul,

369
00:18:57,207 --> 00:18:58,876
- Eon Byul.
- but who is Eun Dol?

370
00:18:58,877 --> 00:19:01,017
Eun Byul's reckless side.

371
00:19:01,347 --> 00:19:02,617
- It was unexpected.
- Eun Dol.

372
00:19:02,847 --> 00:19:05,017
I must have mixed up the words there.

373
00:19:05,157 --> 00:19:07,216
- That's how she became Eun Dol?
- Reckless Eun Byul.

374
00:19:07,217 --> 00:19:08,256
