- Eun Dol.

375
00:19:08,257 --> 00:19:10,486
I believe this one will be pretty influential.

376
00:19:10,487 --> 00:19:11,656
- Very.
- Right?

377
00:19:11,657 --> 00:19:13,426
- They're talking in private.
- And late at night.

378
00:19:13,427 --> 00:19:14,467
Yes.

379
00:19:16,927 --> 00:19:17,967
Thank you.

380
00:19:26,007 --> 00:19:27,107
- So, - Yes.

381
00:19:28,477 --> 00:19:30,107
How was the date today?

382
00:19:30,347 --> 00:19:31,417
Today?

383
00:19:31,847 --> 00:19:34,177
