- Yes.

384
00:19:34,487 --> 00:19:36,417
It wasn't so bad. I liked it.

385
00:19:39,787 --> 00:19:42,187
I feel like we got closer.

386
00:19:42,987 --> 00:19:44,556
I think you certainly get closer...

387
00:19:44,557 --> 00:19:46,757
- after a 1-on-1 date.
- Right.

388
00:19:49,967 --> 00:19:52,537
She naturally played along with my jokes.

389
00:19:59,137 --> 00:20:01,247
How was your date today?

390
00:20:01,407 --> 00:20:02,447
My date?

391
