I didn't think it was too bad.

392
00:20:09,247 --> 00:20:12,557
But compared to the date yesterday,

393
00:20:12,987 --> 00:20:14,787
- the atmosphere...
- The atmosphere?

394
00:20:15,357 --> 00:20:18,056
