400
00:20:31,207 --> 00:20:33,277
I don't think she's complimenting Jae Seung!

401
00:20:33,907 --> 00:20:35,506
- I mean...
- You don't think so?

402
00:20:35,507 --> 00:20:36,976
I'm tearing up.

403
00:20:36,977 --> 00:20:38,117
(Tears are falling.)

404
00:20:39,377 --> 00:20:43,987
(The dates with the two men felt different.)

405
00:20:45,287 --> 00:20:48,927
So, I was like, "What is this?"

406
00:20:49,987 --> 00:20:52,157
You two were so different...

407
00:20:52,357 --> 00:20:54,627
that I almost couldn't believe it.

408
00:20:57,827 --> 00:21:00,196
- He's the quiet one, - Yes.

409
00:21:00,197 --> 00:21:03,166
- and I'm the loud one?
- I wouldn't say you were loud.

410
00:21:03,167 --> 00:21:04,407
Yesterday,

411
00:21:05,337 --> 00:21:06,407
it was a bit...

412
00:21:09,707 --> 00:21:11,816
I had a lot of fun.

413
00:21:11,817 --> 00:21:14,647
(I had a lot of fun yesterday.)

414
00:21:16,087 --> 00:21:17,247
I also had fun.

415
00:21:20,357 --> 00:21:22,356
Eun Byul really mustered up her courage there.

416
00:21:22,357 --> 00:21:23,386
Yes.

417
00:21:23,387 --> 00:21:25,797
(Timid Eun Byul shows courage.)

418
00:21:29,597 --> 00:21:31,997
(Staring)

419
00:21:32,437 --> 00:21:34,366
- Can I try on your glasses?
- Sure.

420
00:21:34,367 --> 00:21:36,006
- Do they have lenses?
- Yes.

421
00:21:36,007 --> 00:21:37,807
These are prescription lenses.

422
00:21:41,137 --> 00:21:42,646
- It suits you.
- Does it?

423
00:21:42,647 --> 00:21:44,006
(It suits you.)

424
00:21:44,007 --> 00:21:45,147
Is there a mirror?

425
00:21:45,317 --> 00:21:46,647
It looks good on you.

426
00:21:50,117 --> 00:21:51,457
Do I look like a studying man?

427
00:21:54,417 --> 00:21:56,057
(Swaggering)

428
00:21:58,027 --> 00:22:00,457
You could at least hold the pencil right.

429
00:22:01,527 --> 00:22:03,897
I've only held pencils this way.

430
00:22:05,197 --> 00:22:06,667
Shouldn't you do this?

431
00:22:07,137 --> 00:22:08,166
Do you mean this?

432
00:22:08,167 --> 00:22:11,337
