433
00:22:11,707 --> 00:22:13,537
- Right?
- I used to do that a lot.

434
00:22:14,237 --> 00:22:16,146
I've always been curious about this.

435
00:22:16,147 --> 00:22:17,447
Oh, me too!

436
00:22:17,547 --> 00:22:19,077
I've always wanted to try it.

437
00:22:20,147 --> 00:22:22,246
- Should we try it?
- Should we?

438
00:22:22,247 --> 00:22:23,417
