444
00:22:34,967 --> 00:22:36,427
- I'm...
- That was...

445
00:22:36,697 --> 00:22:38,567
- I'm so embarrassed.
- Try again.

446
00:22:38,837 --> 00:22:40,266
I wonder if it's...

447
00:22:40,267 --> 00:22:42,737
