448
00:22:44,107 --> 00:22:46,237
- Get ready for the next step.
- Okay.

449
00:22:46,737 --> 00:22:47,906
Hold on.

450
00:22:47,907 --> 00:22:48,907
(Laughing)

451
00:22:48,908 --> 00:22:51,047
- How do I do it?
- Just...

452
00:22:52,947 --> 00:22:55,147
