- I don't know.

454
00:22:57,387 --> 00:22:58,587
Do you want to keep it?

455
00:23:01,357 --> 00:23:03,087
- It says, "Thank you." - That's it?

456
00:23:04,857 --> 00:23:06,297
I feel like it's mocking us.

457
00:23:07,327 --> 00:23:08,727
- Right?
- "Thank you!"

458
00:23:09,397 --> 00:23:11,997
Why is this so funny? Gosh.

459
00:23:13,897 --> 00:23:16,237
I talked to Eun Byul a lot,

460
00:23:16,737 --> 00:23:17,906
and we were vibing.

461
00:23:17,907 --> 00:23:20,337
It reminded me of the date from yesterday,

462
00:23:20,877 --> 00:23:21,977
so it felt good.

463
00:23:26,177 --> 00:23:27,747
I was going to do it, but...

464
00:23:31,187 --> 00:23:33,687
Out of everything that happened today,

465
00:23:33,987 --> 00:23:36,887
the time I spent with Jae Hyuk at the end...

466
00:23:37,227 --> 00:23:40,027
was really amusing.

467
00:23:40,357 --> 00:23:42,227
It stuck with me.

468
00:23:43,767 --> 00:23:45,936
I kind of want to focus...

469
00:23:45,937 --> 00:23:49,237
on one person in the remaining time.

470
00:23:51,037 --> 00:23:53,307
So, starting today,

471
00:23:53,607 --> 00:23:57,146
I wish I could spend as much time with him as possible.

472
00:23:57,147 --> 00:23:59,246
(With Jae Hyuk)

473
00:23:59,247 --> 00:24:02,286
This is incredible.

474
00:24:02,287 --> 00:24:05,916
Sung Mi can't stop smiling right now.

475
00:24:05,917 --> 00:24:06,986
She's right next to me,

476
00:24:06,987 --> 00:24:08,486
- and it's...
- She's sealing the deal.

477
00:24:08,487 --> 00:24:10,986
