- That's true.
- One of the players.

492
00:24:37,447 --> 00:24:39,286
- He's playing differently.
- Seo Yoon is.

493
00:24:39,287 --> 00:24:40,956
- No, I mean Jae Hyuk.
- Jae Hyuk is?

494
00:24:40,957 --> 00:24:44,456
Jae Hyuk is the one committing a foul.

495
00:24:44,457 --> 00:24:46,827
- He can't do that.
- He shouldn't.

496
00:24:47,097 --> 00:24:48,166
- Is this all right?
- Yes.

497
00:24:48,167 --> 00:24:49,167
Okay.

498
00:24:49,168 --> 00:24:51,767
(While Eun Byul and Jae Hyuk make memories, )

499
00:24:52,697 --> 00:24:55,237
(Seo Yoon, who went on a date with Jae Hyuk, )

500
00:24:56,467 --> 00:25:01,807
(goes to bed early.)

501
00:25:04,447 --> 00:25:06,947
Is she in the right mind?

502
00:25:07,347 --> 00:25:09,646
- She shouldn't be in bed!
- Exactly.

503
00:25:09,647 --> 00:25:11,046
They're going all out right above you.

504
00:25:11,047 --> 00:25:13,857
- Exactly. You shouldn't be in bed.
- You shouldn't.

505
00:25:14,117 --> 00:25:16,457
I don't think she saw it coming.

506
00:25:16,557 --> 00:25:18,296
That's why they can't sleep.

507
00:25:18,297 --> 00:25:20,027
They have to pull an all-nighter.

508
00:25:20,857 --> 00:25:22,227
An all-nighter!

509
00:25:22,467 --> 00:25:24,126
- That's amazing.
- You don't get to sleep!

510
00:25:24,127 --> 00:25:25,936
- I haven't heard that in a while.
- It goes on for several days.

511
00:25:25,937 --> 00:25:27,257
How would they stay up all night?

512
00:25:27,767 --> 00:25:29,507
- You can't leave your post.
- Exactly.

513
00:25:29,937 --> 00:25:34,807
(Meanwhile, in the kitchen)

514
00:25:34,847 --> 00:25:36,247
There's Yu Bin.

515
00:25:36,577 --> 00:25:38,177
Are you guys eating something again?

516
00:25:39,547 --> 00:25:41,016
- Do you want this?
- Yes.

517
00:25:41,017 --> 00:25:44,957
(Yu Bin and Hoo are in the kitchen without fail.)

518
00:25:46,717 --> 00:25:50,057
I felt bad that I didn't get to go on a date with him today.

519
00:25:50,257 --> 00:25:53,597
And I wanted to ask him how the date went...

520
00:25:53,697 --> 00:25:56,197
and spend some time with him.

521
00:25:57,327 --> 00:26:01,297
(Hoo and Yu Bin sit face-to-face in the hideout.)

522
00:26:02,607 --> 00:26:04,167
How was your date today?

523
00:26:07,207 --> 00:26:09,147
(Thinking)

524
00:26:09,977 --> 00:26:14,177
I think I just got to know who she was.

525
00:26:15,717 --> 00:26:17,947
